  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "This is a minimalist refactoring of the original `gym-pybullet-drones` repository, designed for compatibility with [`gymnasium`](https://github.com/Farama-Foundation/Gymnasium), [`stable-baselines3` 2.0](https://github.com/DLR-RM/stable-baselines3/pull/1327), and [`betaflight`](https://github.com/betaflight/betaflight)/[`crazyflie-firmware`](https://github.com/bitcraze/crazyflie-firmware/) SITL.",
    "context": "This is a minimalist refactoring of the original `gym-pybullet-drones` repository, designed for compatibility with [`gymnasium`](https://github.com/Farama-Foundation/Gymnasium), [`stable-baselines3` 2.0](https://github.com/DLR-RM/stable-baselines3/pull/1327), and [`betaflight`](https://github.com/betaflight/betaflight)/[`crazyflie-firmware`](https://github.com/bitcraze/crazyflie-firmware/) SITL.\n\n> **NOTE**: if you want to access the original codebase, presented at IROS in 2021, please `git checkout [paper|master]`\n\n<img src=\"gym_pybullet_drones/assets/helix.gif\" alt=\"formation flight\" width=\"325\"> <img src=\"gym_pybullet_drones/assets/helix.png\" alt=\"control info\" width=\"425\">",
